## Lead Processing Workflow

Lead generation flow operates through a multi-stage process:

1. Lead Submission
   - Custom dealership-specific workflow processing
   - Sales person association and assignment logic
   - Demo environment routing conditions

2. XML Generation
   - Conversion to ADF (Auto-lead Data Format) compliant structure
   - Integration of dealer-specific requirements
   - Vehicle specification formatting

3. Notification Distribution
   - Dealer CRM system integration
   - Sales person assignment notifications
   - Status update alerts

## Routing Logic

Core routing components:
- Demo environment-specific routing based on dealership assignments
- Sales person association requirements
- Multi-dealership distribution handling

## Lead Status Management

Status progression handling:
- Initial submission validation
- Dealer CRM compatibility verification
- Sales person assignment confirmation
- Lead tracking updates

## Notification Integration

Notification system handles:
- Dealer-specific routing rules
- Sales team assignment broadcasts
- Lead status change alerts
- CRM system synchronization

